cs.CV, cs.MM, cs.LG, cs.GR, cs.IR 

This paper deals with image processing and machine learning techniques for denoising images. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves modeling and training a neural network, which falls under cs.MM (Multimedia). Additionally, the paper discusses the effects of image processing pipeline components, which could be categorized under cs.LG (Machine Learning) or cs.GR (Graphics). Finally, the paper deals with image sensors and raw measurements, which could be classified under cs.IR (Information Retrieval).
